&lt;li&gt;Track and report on program performance, pacing, and sales engagement in partnership with Marketing Ops, Sales Ops, and Strategy, maintaining real-time dashboards and contributing to a global playbook&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
